# grepai-first

> **DEFAULT:** `grepai_search` FIRST for any code search.

| Task | Tool | Scope |
|------|------|-------|
| **⭐ Search by intent/meaning** | **grepai_search** | `[project only]` |
| Exact text/regex | Grep | `[project*]` |
| File path patterns | Glob | `[project*]` |
| External/web | WebSearch | `[internet]` |

`[project*]` = cwd by default, accepts `path` param for other locations

**Decision:** exact text/regex? → Grep/Glob · otherwise → grepai

## MCP Tools

| Tool | Use |
|------|-----|
| `grepai_search` | Semantic: `"auth flow"`, `"error handling"` |
| `grepai_trace_callers` | Functions calling symbol |
| `grepai_trace_callees` | Functions called by symbol |
| `grepai_trace_graph` | Full call graph around symbol |
| `grepai_index_status` | Index health/stats |

## Query Tips

- English queries (better semantic matching)
- Intent over syntax: `"handles login"` not `"func Login"`
- Specific: `"JWT validation"` not `"token"`
